<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Busta Rhymes was revealed to be the Dragon on the Season 4 premiere of The Masked Singer, which aired Wednesday on FOX.</p>

<p>The 48-year-old singer, known for hits like Dangerous and Don't Cha, with the Pussycat Dolls, had underwhelmed voters with his cover of LL Cool J's Mama Said Knock You Out.</p>

<p>When he unmasked, he said that wearing the dragon costume made him feel like he was 'in an oxygen tank without oxygen.'</p>

